comment_regular_data.body: This is mainly here to keep it in mind. This still needs some work I hope @JFreegman can help with.
Where is the design doc / stuff?
When will be rewiew and integration new groupchats?
@alexeysvrv currently, the soonest will be after I fix `net_crypto` I have no eta on that as there's a list of other things I need to finish first.
What's the state if this one?
Current state: limbo. No news to report.

Still needs net_crypto to be fixed.

I'm working on that, but my understanding is that there are no plans to merge those fixes to toktok
Looking forward to the merging day.
Please close this PR because it is outdated and doesn't work. It's confusing to keep old broken PR's like this.
This PR is no longer under active development. For new development, see #847. If you'd like to contribute, please contact @ingvar1995 or come chat on `#toktok` on Freenode IRC.
I argee with @ingvar1995 if you want to keep it for archival uses; consider merging it into `archive/branchname` and closing this pull. Any open PR should be for work in progress...

commit.message:
Avoid 0-sized VLA allocations.

These are undefined behaviour. In one case, we do nothing, in the other
case we use malloc, since `malloc(0)` is valid.
